--- !u!114 &8688350936388443906
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1605598397388320318}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f99d277d073513e41b17436db9f0b404, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  prompt_description: 'In this game, player can spend 3 manas to use cards on each
    turn. Cards represent protagonist''s actions.

    Most cards cost 1 mana. Very
    powerful moves will cost 2 or 3 mana. 0-mana cards represent swift but weaker
    moves.

    The effects of a card include dealing damage to target, healing the
    user, adding tacks of "block" (blocking same amount of upcoming damage), applying
    buff to user or casting debuff to targets.

    Typically, one cost cards are
    worth 5 damage, or 5 stacks of block, or 3 stacks of buff/debuff. Cards with
    higher rarity can be stronger.



    The protagonist is ##HeroName##, ##HeroDesc##.
    Now I need you to generate the starting deck for the player.

    The starting
    deck contains 4 copies of a basic attack card, 4 copies of a basic defence(blocking)
    card, 2 copies of a special supporting card, and 2 copies of a special offence
    card.

    Please consider what''s the hero''s play style in a turn-based card
    game.

    Please also design the illustration of these cards. They should look
    unique and distinctive in colors and other visual elements.

    Please tell
    me with natural language, what could be the name, narrative design, visual, and
    the effect in gameplay of those 4 unique cards.'
  prompt_effects: "Please briefly introduce custom effects (buffs/debuffs) that could
    be brought by these ##Rarity## cards. \nFor example: \nStrength: increase the
    amount of damage directly dealt by the character one per stack; \nBurn: deal
    damage to the owner one per stack at the start of each turn, and lower the damage
    dealt by the owner one per stack."
  prompt_basicCard1: "Now please specify the design of the basic attack card.\r\nPlease
    reply with following json format: (content in parentheses are comments)\r\n{\r\n\t\"cardName\":
    \"Punch\",\r\n\t\"description\": \"Punch the targeted enemy with mighty power.\",\r\n\t\"manaCost\":
    1,\r\n\t\"needTarget\": true,\r\n\t\"prompt\": \"Punch, dynamic, sense of power,
    big fist, single fist with sense of power,\" (prompt for Stable Diffusion card
    image generation. Try describe a dynamic action, emphasizing the attacking intention)
    \r\n}"
  prompt_basicCard2: "Now please specify the design of the basic defence(blocking)
    card.\r\nPlease reply with following json format: (content in parentheses are
    comments)\r\n{\r\n\t\"cardName\": \"Arcane Barrier\",\r\n\t\"description\": \"Focus
    arcane energy to form a barrier, neutralizing upcoming damage.\",\r\n\t\"manaCost\":
    1,\r\n\t\"needTarget\": false,(if this card need a single enemy as target)\r\n\t\"prompt\":
    \"Arcane Barrier, magical power, blue sphere, blue aura, magical,\" (prompt for
    Stable Diffusion card image generation. Try describe a dynamic action. Images
    of different cards should look unique and distinctive, in colors and other visual
    elements.) \n}"
  prompt_basicCard3: "Now please specify the design of the special supporting card.\r\nPlease
    reply with following json format: (content in parentheses are comments)\r\n{\r\n\t\"cardName\":
    \"Energy Charge\",\r\n\t\"description\": \"Charge up electro energy, enpower
    future attacks in this game.\",\r\n\t\"manaCost\": 2,\r\n\t\"needTarget\": false,
    (if this card need a single enemy as target)\r\n\t\"prompt\": \"Charging Energy,
    gathering energy, cybernetic,\" (prompt for Stable Diffusion card image generation.
    Try not include character in card image and describe a dynamic action.  Images
    of different cards should look unique and distinctive, in colors and other visual
    elements.) \r\n}"
  prompt_basicCard4: "Now please specify the design of the special offensive card.\r\nPlease
    reply with following json format: (content in parentheses are comments)\r\n{\r\n\t\"cardName\":
    \"Arcane Cascade\",\r\n\t\"description\": \"Spend a huge amount of arcane energy,
    deal a lot of damage to all enemies.\",\r\n\t\"manaCost\": 3,\r\n\t\"needTarget\":
    false, (if this card need a single enemy as target)\r\n\t\"prompt\": \"Arcane
    Cascade, huge barrage with magical shoots, magical attack,\" (prompt for Stable
    Diffusion card image generation. Try describe a dynamic action. Images of different
    cards should look unique and distinctive, in colors and other visual elements)
    \r\n}"
  rareCardCnt: 3
  prompt_rareDescription: 'Now I need you to design the rare cards for the hero ##HeroName##,
    ##HeroDesc##.

    You need to design ##Total## rare cards. They should cover
    different intents (attack, defense, strengthening, resources, support, etc.),
    and different costs.

    These rare cards can be slightly stronger and more
    creatively designed than the basic cards, and their effects can be compounded,
    while not overpowered.

    Please think about the hero''s narrative and play
    style in this game before designing.

    Please also design the illustration
    of these cards. They should look unique and distinctive in colors and other visual
    elements.

    Describe your process of synthesizing and designing these rare
    cards, and then describe the design of ##Total## cards in natural language. Don''t
    reply with json.'
  prompt_rareCard: "Now I need you to specify the design of ##Number## out of ##Total##
    rare cards.\r\n\r\nPlease reply with following json format: (content in parentheses
    are comments)\r\n{\r\n\t\"cardName\": \"Magic Augmentation\",\r\n\t\"description\":
    \"Double the effect of the next magic card played in this turn.\",\r\n\t\"manaCost\":
    0,\r\n\t\"needTarget\": false, (if this card need a single enemy as target)\r\n\t\"prompt\":
    \"magical power, magic chanting, huge energy flow\" (prompt for Stable Diffusion
    card image generation. Images of different cards should look unique and distinctive,
    in colors and other visual elements.) \r\n}\r\n"
  rareCards: []
  epicCardCnt: 3
  prompt_epicDescription: 'Now I need you to design the epic cards for the hero ##HeroName##,
    ##HeroDesc##.

    You need to design ##Total## epic cards. They should cover
    different intents (attack, defense, strengthening, resources, support, etc.),
    and different costs.

    Epic cards can be slightly stronger, with wilder designs,
    and emphasize the playstyle of the hero, while not overpowered.


    Please
    think about the hero''s narrative and play style in this game before designing.

    Please
    also design the illustration of these cards. They should look unique and distinctive
    in colors and other visual elements.

    Describe your process of synthesizing
    and designing these rare cards, and then describe the design of ##Total## cards
    in natural language. Don''t reply with json.'
  prompt_epicCard: "Now I need you to specify the design of ##Number## out of ##Total##
    epic cards.\r\n\r\nPlease reply with following json format: (content in parentheses
    are comments)\r\n{\r\n\t\"cardName\": \"Magic Augmentation\",\r\n\t\"description\":
    \"Double the effect of the next magic card played in this turn.\",\r\n\t\"manaCost\":
    0,\r\n\t\"needTarget\": false, (if this card need a single enemy as target)\r\n\t\"prompt\":
    \"magical power, magic chanting, huge energy flow\" (prompt for Stable Diffusion
    card image generation. Images of different cards should look unique and distinctive,
    in colors and other visual elements.) \r\n}\r\n"
  epicCards: []
  legendCardCnt: 3
  prompt_legendDescription: 'Now I need you to design the legendary cards for the
    hero ##HeroName##, ##HeroDesc##.

    You need to design ##Total## legendary
    cards. They should cover different intents (attack, defense, strengthening, resources,
    support, etc.), and different costs.

    Legendary cards should be most powerful
    (this does not mean they have higher costs), and most tasteful in term of playstyles,
    while not breaking the balance of the game.


    Please think about the hero''s
    narrative and play style in this game before designing.

    Please also design
    the illustration of these cards. They should look unique and distinctive in colors
    and other visual elements.

    Describe your process of synthesizing and designing
    these rare cards, and then describe the design of ##Total## cards in natural
    language. Don''t reply with json.'
  prompt_legendCard: "Now I need you to specify the design of ##Number## out of ##Total##
    legendary cards.\r\n\r\nPlease reply with following json format: (content in
    parentheses are comments)\r\n{\r\n\t\"cardName\": \"Magic Augmentation\",\r\n\t\"description\":
    \"Double the effect of the next magic card played in this turn.\",\r\n\t\"manaCost\":
    0,\r\n\t\"needTarget\": false, (if this card need a single enemy as target)\r\n\t\"prompt\":
    \"magical power, magic chanting, huge energy flow\" (prompt for Stable Diffusion
    card image generation. Images of different cards should look unique and distinctive,
    in colors and other visual elements.) \r\n}\r\n"
  legendCards: []
  cardGenerated: 0
